<div class="container non-home">
<div class="tabbable">
  <ul id="sub-tabs" class="nav nav-tabs ">
    <% @platforms.each do |page| %>
      <li <% if page.slug == "Go" %>class="active" <% end %>>
        <a href="#<%= page.slug %>" data-toggle="tab"><p><%= page.title %></p></a>
      </li>
    <% end %>
      <li class="active">
	<a href="#GO" data-toggle="tab"><p>Full Platform: Project GO</p></a>
      </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="tab-content">
    <% @platforms.each do |page| %>
      <% if page.slug == "Go" %>
        <div id="<%= page.slug %>" class="hero-unit tab-pane active">
          <h1></h1>
          <p></p>
          <p style="padding-top:40px;">
          </p>
          <div class="well" style="padding-left:55px;">

          </div>
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <div id="<%= page.slug %>" class="hero-unit tab-pane">
          <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
          <hr class="long" />
          <%= page.text %>
          <% page.sections.each do |section| %>
            <div class="well">
              <div class="row">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#<%= section.slug %>" class="nodec">
                  <h2 class="pull-right"><%= section.title %></h2>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="collapse" id="<%=section.slug%>">
                <%= section.text %>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

        <div id="GO" class="hero-unit tab-pane active">
          <p style="padding-top:40px">Below, you’ll find Go Party’s Platform: Project Go. We’ve listed a series of problems, accompanied by solutions and a strategic plan for how we’ll be successful. For a shorter list of our proposed initiatives, categorized by subject, feel free to click on any of the tabs above.</p>
          <p style="padding-bottom:40px">Think of this as our blueprint for action, because from day one, we’ll be ready to go.

</p>
          <div class="well" style="padding-left:55px;">
            <a href="go.pdf" style="color:green">
              <img class="pull-right"
              src="http://www2.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/pdf-icon.png"
               style="max-height:60px"/>
              <h1 class="">Open Project Go Here</h1>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
